::DeathStorm::

DeathStorm blinks in surprise. This was strange. He looks at Grimlock. The 
Grimlock that he had read about was a giant. This one was maximal size. He 
shakes his head.

"There were no other stasis pods falling. At least none that the scanners 
picked up."
